sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import CommonHeader from "./CommonHeader"; import Title from "./Title"; import Footer from "./Footer"; import classes from "./ContactUs.module.css" const ContactUs=()=>{ return <section> <form className={classes.form}> <div className={classes.box}> <label htmlFor="name">Name</label> <input type="text" id="name"/></div> <div className={classes.box}> <label htmlFor="email">Email Id</label> <input type="email" id="email"/></div> <div className={classes.box}> <label htmlFor="phno">Phone Number</label> <input type="number" id="phno"/></div> <button type="submit">Submit</button> </form> </section> <Footer/> </React.Fragment> } export default ContactUs;
